            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_46gc' title='Col. 46GC &mdash; HL Deb 25 November 1996 vol 576 c46GC' name='column_46gc' href='#column_46gc' rel='bookmark'>46GC</a>
            consultation period. These were matters which must have been deliberated upon and yet we are in a situation which does not carry us very much further.</p><p>
